plot: The Critic takes a look at the horrible sequel to the 1999 found-footage smash hit, The Blair Witch Project. He likes the original, but finds the sequel incoherent, horribly acted, badly edited and dreadfully acted.
title: "The Nostalgia Critic" Blair Witch 2: Book of Shadows
